text: Saint-Pierre-la-Vieille is a former commune. It is found in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Condé-en-Normandie.Arrêté préfectoral 1 December 2015 == Related pages == * Communes of the Calvados department == References == Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Saint-Pierre-la-Vieille
